law.catch_line: Transportation Cabinet's approval of analysis required.
law.text: The Transportation Cabinet shall approve the laboratory analysis report as to its conformity with the standards required by KRS 17.310 to 17.340, and no hydraulic brake fluid shall be sold in this state after September 1, 1960, unless such approval has been granted.
law.history: Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 74, Art. V, sec. 24(17). -- Created 1960 Ky. Acts ch. 116, sec. 5, effective June 16, 1960.
